Get mad so you can leave!       

45:52.182 --> 45:54.617
 Stop. No, just stop.         
 So you can leave.            
And I'm not sick!               

45:54.751 --> 45:57.086
 Then what the hell is this,  
Tia?                            
 I'm not sick. I don't know.  

45:57.221 --> 46:00.923
 Huh?!                        
I am sick of this roller-coaster
ride!                           

46:01.058 --> 46:03.192
 Fine.                        
You know what, cool.            
I-I'll just leave. I'll go.     

46:03.327 --> 46:05.461
 No, I'm not say--            
I'm not saying it --            
 I'll leave.                  

46:05.596 --> 46:11.834
 No, no, no, no, no. Stop.    
 Don't put your hands on me!  
You trying to kill me?          

46:11.969 --> 46:15.037
I knew it.                      
Stay away from me.              
Stay away from me!              

46:15.172 --> 46:17.039
 What the hell, Tia?          
No, I'm not --                  
 I will not let you hurt me!  

46:17.174 --> 46:20.877
Stay away from me!              
 Would you -- who are you     
calling?                        

46:21.011 --> 46:22.245
Would you stop?                 
 Hello?                       
 Hang on.                     

46:22.379 --> 46:24.547
 Hello, can you please get to 
