 Tia!                         

46:28.785 --> 46:31.354
 Can you please hurry up?     
 What?                        
 We're -- we're on 1617       

46:31.488 --> 46:33.956
Fallon -- Fallon Lake Circle.   
 What? Hey!                   
 Please come.                 

46:34.091 --> 46:38.928
Hurry up, 'cause I'm scared.    
I'm really scared.              
Please come. I'm scared.        

46:39.062 --> 46:42.298
Please. [ Crying ] Please.      

46:46.403 --> 46:50.339
Please.                         
 [ Sighs ]                    

46:52.709 --> 46:56.345
[ Siren whoops ]                
 Officers, hey.               
I'm sorry about this.           

46:56.480 --> 46:58.614
There's been a really --        
 That's him.                  
That's him, officers.           

46:58.749 --> 47:00.917
 Are you serious?             
 That's my husband that tried 
to kill me.                     

47:01.051 --> 47:02.885
 Wait, wait, wait.            
No, no, no, no.                 
 That's him.                  

47:03.020 --> 47:05.021
 Look, this is a              
misunderstanding.               
My wife isn't well.             

47:05.155 --> 47:08.024
 That's him.                  
 Tia, tell them.              
[ Grunts ]                      

47:08.158 --> 47:10.459
Please. Come on.                
Just -- just listen to me.      
 He tried to grab me, and I-I 

47:10.594 --> 47:12.695
lunged back, and then -- and    
then he...                      
 What are you telling them?   

47:12.829 --> 47:16.666
What are you telling them?      
Tia, come on.                   
Officer, will you just -- just  

47:16.800 --> 47:21.871
talk to her, please?            
This is a misunder-- this is a  
mistake.                        

47:22.005 --> 47:24.740
 I don't know.                
He, um...                       
He just lunged.                 

47:24.875 --> 47:27.977
And I [Stammering]              
 Come on, Tia.                
 Thank you.                   

47:28.111 --> 47:30.813
 Tia!                         
 Thank you for coming.        
Okay, good.                     

47:30.948 --> 47:34.617
Th-thank you.                   
Thank you so much.              
Thank you.                      

47:34.751 --> 47:40.656
Thank you.                      
Don't -- don't let him out.     
Don't let him out.              

47:54.371 --> 47:57.440
[ Whimpering ] Mnh-mnh. Mnh-mnh.
[ Voices whispering ]           
Mnh-mnh.                        

47:57.574 --> 48:01.510
Mnh-mnh.                        
Mnh-mnh.                        
Don't tell me that.             

48:01.645 --> 48:05.581
No.                             
No. Mnh-mnh.                    
I know I don't believe you.     

48:12.823 --> 48:25.434
Makes me want my grandpa back.  
I just want my grandpa back.    
Can I go with you? Please?      

48:25.569 --> 48:31.507
Please. I'm just tired.         
I'm so tired.                   
