 He's where?                  

49:04.057 --> 49:07.626
 Mom was right about him.     
I had him arrested for trying to
kill me.                        

49:07.761 --> 49:11.163
He's the one who killed grandpa.
Him and Paul Bernstein.         
Then they tried to kill me      

49:11.298 --> 49:13.766
together, and I was like,       
