49:20.774 --> 49:26.879
 I see.                       
Uh, sweetie...                  
So, I was thinking that, why    

49:27.014 --> 49:31.317
don't you suspend your campaign 
a bit?                          
Just until the dust settles?    

49:31.451 --> 49:36.122
 Mm, no. No.                  
Grandpa told me not to quit.    
And he's here.                  

49:36.256 --> 49:40.693
Grandpa's here.                 
Do you see him?                 
He told me I could come         

49:40.827 --> 49:42.795
with him.                       
