 Let go of -- you do it.      
 Get your hands off --        

50:24.638 --> 50:26.772
 Hey!                         
 Ma, chill.                   
 Come on.                     

50:26.907 --> 50:32.411
 Don't have time for that.    
Reading. And books.             
